Products.Name: Gelativo Sorbet Passionfruit
Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Gelativo Sorbet Passionfruit' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
Beat the heat this summer, impress your friends, family, dinner guests with refreshing sorbet! Perfect for scooping, for serving in a cone or as an accompaniment for a fruit dessert. Made with real fruit, the deliciously zesty and tangy sweet passionfruit flavour will leave your cheeks tingling and tastebuds dancing without feeling guilty. 99% fat free and great nutritional appeal with real fruit! No added colours or flavours here, let your tastebuds determine for itself. Look no further, gluten and dairy free means this is the sweet treat for those with lactose intolerant diets and sensitive stomachs.

Features:

- 99% Fat Free

- Gluten Free

- Dairy Free

- Real Fruit

- No Added Colours or Flavours
